  <brief_title>Transition From Acute to Chronic Pain After Inguinal Hernia, Hysterectomy and Thoracotomy: Analysis of Risk Factors and Association With Genetic Polymorphisms</brief_title>
  <official_title>Transition From Acute to Chronic Pain After Inguinal Hernia, Hysterectomy and Thoracotomy : Analysis of Risk Factors and Association With Genetic Polymorphisms</official_title>
  <sponsors>
